    <title>Save Document</title>
  </properties>

  <body>
    <section name="Save Document">
      <span class="shortdesc">How to save the changes you made to a document.</span>

   <script type="text/javascript">
    leftpx=155;
    bottompx=225;
   </script>
   <div class='group'> 
    <div id='screenshot'><div>
     <img src="../../../../images/screenshots/cms_M13/contribs/save_document.png" alt='save document screenshot'/> 
    </div></div> 
     <p>
      Persisting the changes to document 'multibazaar2009', by pressing
      'save'.
     </p>
   </div>

   <p>
      After <a href='../concepts/editing.html'>editing</a> a document
      (e.g. <a href='./fill_markuped_text_in_document.html'>writing marked-up text</a>),
      click the 'save' or the 'done' button to save your draft as
      preview version of your document.
    </p>
    <p>
      The save button does nothing else, while the 'done' button will also
      leave <a href='../concepts/edit_mode.html'>edit_mode</a> and
      bring the document in <a href='../concepts/review_mode.html'>review_mode</a>.
    </p>
    <p>
      Even if you do not press the 'save' button, your changes are saved automatically,
      but in the draft version of your document.
      You can <a href='discard_changes.html'>discard the draft</a> version of your
      document, but you can not discard the preview version of your document.
    </p>

